# Game Mechanics

## Collision

- Player cannot move through: buildings, bridges, walls
- Use Mapbox building polygons or custom no-go zones
- Projectiles: hit zombies, may bounce/penetrate based on weapon

## Weapons & Projectiles

- Different weapons = different bullet patterns (spread, burst, homing, etc.)
- Items drop from zombies; can evolve or modify bullet behavior

## Spawn

- Zombies spawn around player (radius-based)
- Spawn rate/config from backend or local config

## Save Position

- Trigger: every 5 minutes OR keyboard shortcut (e.g. `S` or `F5`)
- Payload: `{ lat, lng, userId }`
- Load on game start from last saved position
